These are Puzzles for 3x6 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 3x6-Level-1-1::.
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, alhambra, old-henry, oliveros, blend, baccarat
6 different games are played: monopoly, canasta, poker, scrabble, billiard, go
There are 6 different nationalities: american, chinese, german, malaysian, pakistani, polish
 1. the oliveros-smoker is on the right of the malaysian##1
 2. the old-henry-smoker is on the left of the oliveros-smoker##1
 3. the person playing scrabble is the polish##1
 4. the pakistani is on the far left##1
 5. the dunhill-smoker is on the left of the american##1
 6. the oliveros-smoker is the chinese##1
 7. the american is the person playing canasta##1
 8. the person playing go is on the left of the person playing poker##1
 9. the person playing poker is on the far right##1
10. the person playing billiard is on the right of the blend-smoker##1
11. the oliveros-smoker is on the left of the person playing poker##1
12. the alhambra-smoker is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |   2    |      3      |     4     |    5    |    6    |
| Cigar         | alhambra | dunhill | blend | old-henry   | oliveros  | baccarat |
| Game   | monopoly     | scrabble  | canasta        | billiard      | go  | poker  |
| Nationality   | pakistani   | polish | american    | malaysian | chinese | german  |

