.:: Puzzle 3x6-Level-1-2::.
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: rugby, skiing, parkour, soccer, lacrosse, snowboarding
The people have 6 different jobs:  architect, fisherman, police-officer, project-manager, scientist, snowboardingcher
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: tulip, poppy, zinnia, lily, rose, amaryllis
 1. the snowboardingcher is on the far left##1
 2. the police-officer is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 3. the snowboardingcher is the person who's sport is rugby##1
 4. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
 5. the police-officer is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
 6. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person who growstulip##1
 7. the architect is on the right of the fisherman##1
 8. the person who growspoppy is on the far right##1
 9. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1
10. the person who's sport is skiing is the person who growszinnia##1
11. the person who growsrose is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
12. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the project-manager##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |     3     |        4        |       5        |     6     |
| Sport      | rugby  | soccer | lacrosse    | snowboarding             | skiing           | parkour     |
| Job           | snowboardingcher | fisherman     | architect | project-manager | police-officer | scientist |
| Flower   | lily | amaryllis          | tulip  | rose         | zinnia         | poppy  |

