.:: Puzzle 3x6-Level-1-3::.
The people have 6 different jobs:  designer, videographer, doctor, dressmaker, accountant, coach
There 6 different types of food: apricot, peas, pineapple, pomegranate, tomato, watermelon
The people have 6 different hobbies: collecting, gardening, drawing, singing, traveling, writing
 1. the person eating pineapple is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 2. the coach is on the right of the person eating apricot##1
 3. the accountant is the person eating watermelon##1
 4. the dressmaker is on the far left##1
 5. the person who's hobby is traveling is the person eating tomato##1
 6. the dressmaker is the person eating tomato##1
 7. the dressmaker is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
 8. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person eating pomegranate##1
 9. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the doctor##1
10. the person eating tomato is on the left of the videographer##1
11. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
12. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the coach##1
13. the person eating pomegranate is on the left of the person eating pineapple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |    3     |       4       |     5     |     6      |
| Job      | dressmaker | videographer | coach | doctor | designer       | accountant    |
| Food          | tomato   | apricot     | peas     | pomegranate   | pineapple | watermelon |
| Hobby   | traveling     | writing      | singing     | drawing           | collecting   | gardening       |

