.:: Puzzle 3x6-Level-1-4::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: animation, crime, mystery, sports, thriller, zombie
6 different games are played: canasta, domino, bridge, whist, go, billiard
There are 6 different favourite colors: yellow, chestnut, apricot, emerald, ebony, amber
 1. the person playing whist is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1
 2. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
 3. the person watching crime movies is the person who likes yellow##1
 4. the person playing domino is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
 5. the person who likes amber is on the far right##1
 6. the person playing go is on the right of the person playing domino##1
 7. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person who likes ebony##1
 8. the person playing whist is on the left of the person who likes amber##1
 9. the person watching animation movies is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
10. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
11. the person watching animation movies is on the left of the person who likes emerald##1
12. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |    3     |     4     |      5       |     6      |
| Movie-Genre   | crime    | thriller | mystery  | animation | sports       | zombie     |
| Game   | bridge   | canasta  | domino | go   | whist     | billiard    |
| Color         | yellow | ebony  | apricot  | chestnut  | emerald | amber |

