6 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, fonseca, bolivar, havana, blend, vegafina
 1. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 2. the person watching thriller movies is the alhambra-smoker##1
 3. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in march is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 5. the bolivar-smoker is on the far right##1
 6. the person watching family movies is on the far right##1
 7. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the fonseca-smoker##1
 8. the blend-smoker is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the alhambra-smoker##1
10. the fonseca-smoker is the person who's birthday is in june##1
11. the person who's birthday is in august is the vegafina-smoker##1
12. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
13. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |      3       |     4      |      5      |      6      |
| Birthday         | august   | february   | march      | september | june   | may |
| Movie-Genre   | musical | time-travel | martial-arts | thriller   | documentary | family      |
