 3. the fan of ambient is on the right of the tiparillo-smoker##1
 4. the fan of funk is on the right of the fan of folk##1
 5. the fan of funk is on the left of the vegafina-smoker##1
 6. the tiparillo-smoker is on the right of the indian##1
 7. the chinese is on the left of the polish##1
