 9. the fan of classical is on the left of the tiparillo-smoker##1
10. the ritmeester-smoker is on the far left##1
11. the dannemann-smoker is on the left of the dutch##1
12. the prince-smoker is on the left of the vegafina-smoker##1
13. the pall-mall-smoker is on the right of the dannemann-smoker##1
14. the polish is the fan of dubstep##1

.:: Answer ::.
