6 different pets are kept: pony, goldfish, mouse, bird, rat, fish
The people use 6 different means of transport: boat, helicopter, roller, ship, skateboard, taxi
 1. the person driving the ship is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
 2. the person driving the roller is on the left of the alhambra-smoker##1
 3. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
 4. the owner of the fish is on the right of the oliveros-smoker##1
 5. the aristoff-smoker is the owner of the goldfish##1
 6. the owner of the rat is on the left of the old-henry-smoker##1
 7. the owner of the goldfish is on the far right##1
 8. the ritmeester-smoker is the person driving the taxi##1
 9. the pall-mall-smoker is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
10. the person driving the skateboard is the owner of the goldfish##1
11. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
12. the person driving the roller is the owner of the pony##1
13. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |    3    |      4      |   5    |     6      |
| Cigar      | oliveros | pall-mall   | ritmeester | old-henry       | alhambra   | aristoff        |
| Pet   | mouse       | fish | rat | pony | bird | goldfish      |
| Transport     | helicopter    | boat    | taxi    | roller      | ship   | skateboard |

