 3. the person traveling to miami is on the left of the wooden house##1
 4. the person who's sport is baseball is on the far right##1
 5. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
 6. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1
 7. the wooden house is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
 8. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
 9. the wooden house is the person who's sport is baseball##1
10. the art-deco house is on the left of the victorian house##1
11. the cape-cod house is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1
12. the person who's sport is rugby is the art-deco house##1
13. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1

