The people use 6 different means of transport: trike, scooter, airplane, snowmobile, tram, jet-ski
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: animation, comedy, disaster, fantasy, musical, spy
 1. the person watching animation movies is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
 2. the person driving the tram is the fan of ambient##1
 3. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
 4. the person driving the tram is on the right of the fan of disco##1
 5. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 6. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
 7. the person watching disaster movies is on the far left##1
 8. the fan of hip-hop is the person driving the scooter##1
 9. the fan of gospel is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
10. the fan of disco is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
11. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
12. the person driving the trike is the fan of punk##1
13. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
