.:: Puzzle 3x6-Level-1-18::.
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, bongani, havana, game, tiparillo, chaman
6 different pets are kept: chinchilla, ferret, fish, frog, hamster, hedgehog
There are 6 different favourite colors: chestnut, turquise, ebony, amber, emerald, fuchsia
 1. the tiparillo-smoker is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
 2. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the person who likes turquise##1
 3. the owner of the fish is on the far left##1
 4. the person who likes ebony is the bongani-smoker##1
 5. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the person who likes chestnut##1
 6. the person who likes emerald is on the left of the game-smoker##1
 7. the person who likes chestnut is on the far right##1
 8. the game-smoker is on the right of the person who likes emerald##1
 9. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the person who likes amber##1
10. the havana-smoker is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
11. the chaman-smoker is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
12. the person who likes ebony is the owner of the frog##1
13. the baccarat-smoker is on the right of the havana-smoker##1
14. the baccarat-smoker is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |    3    |     4      |    5    |    6    |
| Cigar   | chaman          | game       | bongani | havana       | baccarat | tiparillo     |
| Pet           | fish          | hedgehog   | frog    | chinchilla | ferret  | hamster |
| Color         | emerald | fuchsia | ebony  | amber      | turquise    | chestnut |

