.:: Puzzle 3x6-Level-1-19::.
6 different games are played: chess, domino, poker, mah-jongg, snooker, backgammon
House: wooden, gothic-revival, townhouse, cottage, tower, craftsman
6 different pets are kept: bird, cat, ferret, frog, goldfish, guinea-pig
 1. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the wooden house##1
 2. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
 3. the owner of the cat is on the left of the person playing domino##1
 4. the craftsman house is the person playing backgammon##1
 5. the owner of the bird is the person playing poker##1
 6. the owner of the goldfish is the person playing mah-jongg##1
 7. the cottage house is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
 8. the person playing chess is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
 9. the craftsman house is on the right of the wooden house##1
10. the craftsman house is on the left of the cottage house##1
11. the townhouse house is on the right of the tower house##1
12. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the tower house##1
13. the person playing domino is on the right of the owner of the cat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |    4    |     5     |      6       |
| Game   | snooker   | domino | mah-jongg | backgammon  | chess | poker |
| House   | tower | townhouse     | wooden  | craftsman | cottage  | gothic-revival     |
| Pet           | cat       | guinea-pig  | goldfish   | frog    | ferret    | bird         |

