.:: Puzzle 3x6-Level-1-20::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: 7up, coffee, hot-chocolate, soy-milk, sprite, water
There are 6 different nationalities: australian, malaysian, italian, american, german, british
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: september, november, may, april, february, august
 1. the american is the person who's birthday is in april##1
 2. the british is the person drinking sprite##1
 3. the australian is on the far right##1
 4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person who's birthday is in september##1
 5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far left##1
 6. the american is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the malaysian##1
 8. the german is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in august is on the far left##1
10. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking water##1
11. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
12. the person drinking water is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
13. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
14. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |     3      |       4       |      5       |       6       |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | water    | sprite     | hot-chocolate | coffee       | 7up           |
| Nationality       | german  | italian | british | malaysian     | american       | australian     |
| Birthday      | august  | may   | november    | september       | april | february |

 